---
title: Chimichurri Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Tahini & Garlic Sauce
description: Add tonnes of flavour to your dinner with our new chimichurri seasoning! Herby and with a hint of spice, we've used it
to coat succulent chicken strips. Served with roasted veggies and couscous, it's definitely a meal to remember.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

